                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9326" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0305</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">790 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">借“绿”生“金”助振兴：恒瑞环科沙漠治理中的责任与担当</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Using &quot;Green&quot; to Generate &quot;Gold&quot; to Assist Revitalization: The Responsibility and Responsibility of Hengrui Environmental Science and Technology in Desert Governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈玉宏，魏鹭，董爱荷，高平，张寅（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古鄂尔多斯市恒瑞环科制造有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">环保部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒瑞环科；生物质能；企业社会责任；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hengrui Environmental Science; Biomass energy; Corporate social responsibility; sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“双碳”背景下，可持续发展和环境保护成为社会各主体应履行的共同责任。本案例结合恒瑞环科的具体实践，以综合高效利用沙柳、柠条等林业废弃物为主线，分别描述恒瑞环科通过集中供暖模式取缔传统“燃煤小锅炉”，解决农牧民冬季供暖的民生问题。通过废弃灰泥再利用，有效改良周边沙地、盐碱地质量。通过种植水飞蓟，以“企业+党支部+百姓”的助农新模式带动当地农牧民增收致富的全过程。展现了恒瑞环科在推动乡村振兴过程中的责任与担当，不仅暖了百姓、美了生态，还鼓了钱袋。通过案例分析，旨在引导学院理解企业社会责任的概念、驱动因素、价值创造路径以及利益相关者理论等内容，进而掌握理论中的知识结构与基本要点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of achieving &quot;dual carbon&quot; goals, sustainable development and environmental protection have become the common responsibilities of all social entities. This case combines the specific practices of Hengrui Huanke and describes the entire process of how the company uses the comprehensive and efficient utilization of forestry waste materials such as sandalwood and saltwort as the main line to solve the livelihood problem of farmers and herdsmen in winter heating by replacing traditional &quot;small coal-fired boilers&quot; through the central heating mode. It also describes how the company effectively improves the quality of surrounding sandy and saline soil by recycling waste slag. Furthermore, it describes how the company, through the cultivation of water fleabane, uses the new &quot;enterprise + party branch + people&quot; assistance model to drive local farmers and herdsmen to increase their income and achieve wealth. The case showcases Hengrui Huanke&#39;s sense of responsibility and commitment in driving rural revitalization, not only warming the people, beautifying the ecology, but also enriching their pockets. Through case analysis, the aim is to guide students to understand the concepts of corporate social responsibility, drivers, value creation pathways, and stakeholder theory, thereby mastering the knowledge structure and key points of the theory.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任的概念和驱动因素；战略性企业社会责任价值创造路径；利益相关者理论；可持续发展的核心理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
